  <!-- Fixed-base mount for Gazebo                                     -->
  <!-- Gazebo treats the specially named "world" link as the inertial   -->
  <!-- world. This fixed joint rigidly mounts the arm base to the world -->
  <!-- while leaving all seven actuated joints controllable.            -->
  <!-- It also makes world the URDF root, avoiding the KDL warning about -->
  <!-- an inertial block on the root base_link.                          -->
